We made snowmen. We fought with snowballs. We built forts. We played pretend. We were happy.

Portland, Oregon is a city that is known for being "weird". This is seen in the city's slogan, "Keep Portland Weird". This slogan is on a building that is also a pizza place, a bar, a music club, and a place for dancing. Some people say this slogan is about remembering the old Portland, before it was very popular and expensive.  Others say it is a welcome to people who are different. 

Portland is still weird, even though many rich people from California have moved there and new buildings are being made.  Being weird does not mean accepting everything. It means accepting things that are not normal. Portland has many modern things, like stores that sell things made in China. There are many ways to be different. Portland has people who do yoga, people who are interested in fashion, and people who work in business. Some people say that being weird means not taking things too seriously.

My neighborhood has colorful houses, gardens with flowers, herbs, and vegetables.  During the summer, there are boxes on the streets filled with things for free. These boxes can have anything in them, like clothes, books, or toys. Finding something special in a free box is fun! Portland is about finding the magic in everyday things.

Portland has many different kinds of people. Some people like goat yoga or watching the city's soccer team play. Portland is a place where people follow their dreams. Portland also has problems. Some people have drug problems and some people do not have a place to live. These are problems that many cities have. People in Portland want to help, but it is hard to know what to do.

The mountains are always there. They are in the north. They see the sun each day. I work and live a busy life. I may forget about them. But they are still there. They do not change. They are strong. When I am sad, I look at the mountains. They help me feel better. I first saw the mountains when I went to school. The mountains are near the school. The school is very nice. It has good buildings, ponds, and trees. But the mountains are my favorite. The town is nice too. There are many cafes. I study there. I can walk to the city. The city has old buildings. It is busy. Then I can walk back to the quiet town. The town has two different feels. It is good. I have many memories here. I have good memories and bad memories here. The ponds are good for thinking. I think about life there. I see the turtles, ducks, and insects. I think about my life. I walk to the mountains. The mountains are big and strong. They are in the sky. I feel strong too.

If you go to Bensonhurt, Brooklyn, it is easy to find. Public transportation is good. Bensonhurt is a city neighborhood. You will feel like you are in New York City. You will see many Asian stores. Many Asian people live in Bensonhurt now. You will see an Asian store on every block. Supermarkets and laundromats are very popular. People like these stores. The food is good. The prices are low. It is easy to go shopping. There are four Asian supermarkets near me. They are all close together. This makes it easy to buy food. Bensonhurst has many kinds of people. There are immigrants and their children. Most big stores are owned by Asian people. There is a new park near here. It has basketball courts, a big field for soccer, and a playground for kids. The park has a water fountain too. The park is like New York City. There are many kinds of people. 

There are not many big buildings in Bensonhurst. There are houses for people to live in. Most people are nice. But, they can be noisy. You will hear cars making noise. They play loud music. The cars make noise in the morning. If you visit at night, be careful. Bensonhurst is safe. But, people can be mean. You might meet people who want to fight. There have been problems with stealing packages. 

People do not always clean up after their dogs. You will see dog waste on the ground. This is a problem.

My home is on a big hill. It is very steep. People run up it. There are no sidewalks on my street. People walk on the road. The road is old. It has holes. The wires for phones and electricity are old too. They look bad. There are many tall trees. People do not like the trees. They want to cut them down. They cover the view of the ocean. Many houses are high up on the hill. They have big windows to see the ocean.

The ocean is beautiful at sunset. The water is orange. The sky is orange. It often rains. The air is cloudy. Moss grows on everything. It grows on my car!

There are not many children here. There is a school nearby. Many people are old. They have dogs. The dogs run around.  

There are rabbits too.  They dig in the gardens. My cats like to hunt them. There are also birds.

There are no stores near my home. If I go to the water, there are some places to eat. They sell fish. There is a small beach.

The ocean is not very wide. I can see the other side.

I live in a small town in southern Tennessee. My house is on a street that connects two big roads. We have many cars drive by. My street is quiet. Most of the people who live here have been here a long time. They like to work in their yards. In winter, we go sledding. We live at the corner of the street. We see everyone who drives by. When we see a car we do not know, we look at it. Some people walk for exercise. Some walk their dogs. Kids ride their bikes. 

My wife and I work at home. We have two daughters. They are eleven and fourteen years old. We are at home a lot. We like to play outside. Sometimes we play in the rain. We like to cook outside on our deck. It smells good. 

Many people cut their grass. We can hear lawn mowers from March until October. There are many trees in our neighborhood. It was a wooded area before. We have shade. In fall, we rake and burn the leaves. I like the smell. We do not have much winter. It feels like fall is long. Our garage is at the back of our house. We use the front door when someone knocks. I like to work in the garage. When the doors are open, I feel closer to my neighbors.

It is quiet on holidays. On Thanksgiving, some families have visitors. There are more cars. It is the same on Mother's Day and Christmas. I like to live here. If it were not a through street, it would be perfect.

My town is in the middle of the desert. There is much dirt. People who do not live here may not know how brown everything is. When you see a green lawn, you know the owner spends a lot of money. When I first lived here, houses were far apart. Now there are more houses. The town is growing like a city. This is true for many places. People here are mostly friendly. Like all towns, it has good parts and bad parts. Many older people live in my part of town. This makes it a nice place. There are many big stores here, like Food 4 Less and Smart & Final. If you want small stores with lots of food, you must go somewhere else. Most people in town work in construction. This is because the town is still growing. There is much open space to build. This worries me. I like things the way they are. I left a big city and do not want to go back.

My job is in construction. I put up walls and ceilings. I like living here because of the animals. People come to the desert for many reasons. The desert has a special beauty. The desert has changed the plants and animals that live here. People should learn about the animals and plants to live with them safely. My family and I like the animals. My three children love lizards and bugs. They are always catching them.

There are things to do in town. Victorville is good for families. It is different. If you visit, go to the San Bernardino County Fair. It has many activities. You can also go to Wrightwood to see the mountains covered in snow. You can go skiing there. If you like history, go to the Victor Valley Museum. It has rocks, old things, and things from Native Americans.

My home is a college campus.  I live in a dormitory with many other students.  We are a community.  The campus is also my neighborhood.

Like other neighborhoods, my neighborhood has houses, people, stores, and a park.

First, let us talk about the houses. There are three types of houses: apartments, regular houses, and dormitory houses.

Apartments have many rooms.

Four to six rooms are on each floor.  Two to four people live in each room.  Many apartments have two floors.  This means about twenty people live in each building.

Regular houses are for rent.  Alumni often live in these houses.  There are not many regular houses.

Dormitory houses are for students.  Many students live in these houses.  Two students share each room.

My school has many people from different places and ages.  Staff live in the regular houses.  New students live in dormitory houses.  Older students live in apartments.

The best way to understand my neighborhood is to visit.  There are many stores on campus.  There are places to eat and places to buy things.  

My neighborhood has a park.  It is clean and safe.  Everyone takes care of it.

I live in this neighborhood for ten years. When I first came, I was sad. I moved from Riverdale to Stockbridge. My house in Riverdale was small. My parents wanted a better place for us. Stockbridge is a good place. It has good schools. I made new friends here, but also some enemies.  

I know some of my neighbors. My best neighbors are Mr. Glen and his children and Dennis. They are good people. They are like family. I went to Mr. Glen's wedding. It was fun. 

I like to explore my neighborhood. I have a GPS now, so it is easier. I go to the park. I like to be in nature. It is calm. I bring sticks and practice my balance.

There is a basketball court and a tennis court. I do not play tennis or basketball much, but it is nice to have them. My dad taught me to play tennis with Mr. Graves. We had fun.

I have had a lot of fun in this neighborhood. I think the best is yet to come.

My home is near the college. I like this. There are many apartment buildings. There are also a few small restaurants and bars. They are not very expensive. One bar changed names. Now it is more expensive. The drinks are good. Most people are nice. They are students or have little money. The apartments are cheap. There are many children near my home. There is a school close by. I do not know my neighbors. I do not want to. They smoke a lot of weed. The building managers put a air freshener near their door. My friend and I think this is funny. The buildings are old. Some have new inside parts. There are new apartments down the street. They are expensive. The building work was poor. The rent is high. The buildings are near the college. The managers can charge a lot. There is a cheap restaurant near my home. They serve food on paper plates. Much of the food is heated in the microwave. Across from the restaurant is a gas station. People say it is not a good place to work. The road was fixed last year. Now there is a big sidewalk. There is grass on the sides. The area is better. My building is near many trees. Some trees were cut down. There are more trees where I live than down the street. Behind my building is a line of trees. Then there are more apartments.  My street is 42nd street. Behind my building is 43rd street. It is not as nice. The sidewalks are bad. The buildings look old. There are many trees on this street. They hide the buildings. Most crime in the area is at an apartment complex on this street. But other apartments near me also have crime. I like where I live. It is cheap. There are things I need nearby. I like that the college is close. There are two bus stops. I can go to the store and downtown easily.

My home is in a small group of houses. They look like they are each one house. They are all yellow with white porches and green roofs.

Most people here know each other. We talk at the end of our driveways. The small children play. This is good in our busy world. It is like a simpler time. We have trees and fields. The sky is blue with white clouds.

One problem is we have storms. We had a warning. We heard the sirens. I went to the bathroom with my small dog. My big dog stayed in the living room and barked. It was scary.

After the storm, the ground was wet. The air was hot. The hail melted fast. Then the sun came out and it rained. A rainbow appeared. I took pictures to share with friends and family.

People came home slowly. Then we were back to normal. Children played while dinner cooked. 

I moved here from another place. I like the way people talk here. My house has two bedrooms and two bathrooms. They all look the same outside, but inside they are different. Some are small.

I like to walk to a big field and a small pond. I see deer and hear frogs. It is nice to live here, close to a big city. I hear roosters in the morning. It is like a small village. We even have a donkey nearby.

I am happy to live here.

I go to this area when I was in eighth grade. It was hard to meet people at first. I met two friends. One lives two houses away. The other lives on my street. They do not live here any more. But I still remember them. Most people who lived here when I came still live here. My area is like other areas in America. Many two-story houses are here. I hear kids play outside every weekend when it is warm. My area is quiet most days. I have never had a problem with any people here. You are alone here unless you need help. I have had packages sent to my house. No one has taken them. I trust my neighbors. There is a park near my house. I have many memories there. I played basketball, football, and baseball there with other boys. I got hurt playing football but I had more good times. Now I go to the park to play with my cousin's children. They are younger and like to play on swings and slides. The park makes me feel happy. My area has many different kinds of people. There are many food places. You can find Chinese, Indian, Mexican, and Italian food close by. Many people use services like GrubHub and DoorDash to get food. There are also many fast food places. There are many pizza places. There are many stores here. There are dry cleaners, a Walgreens, a CVS, and a Jewel-Osco grocery store. There is even an Indian store. I like my area. I see bad things happen to people in other areas. I am happy to live here.

My town is small. It is in South Carolina. It is not big. But it is good for farming. My town is called Johnston. It has lots of peach trees.

People say it is the Peach Capital of the World. Most of the town is farms. There are peach trees and cows. Houses are far apart. They are two stories high. Some houses have metal roofs. Some have gray roofs. Houses are not near the road. They are back from the road.

There is one stop light in town. It is at a crossroad. There are some stores near the stop light. There are places to get fast food. There is a Chinese restaurant, a Mexican restaurant, and a burger place. There is a small drug store. It is called Maxwell and Halford Drug. They sell Cherry Coca-Cola.

There is a grocery store called IGA. It is small. People buy things there, but they also go to a Walmart in another town. The most popular store is Dollar General. It sells many things.

There is a furniture store called Possibilities. It is run by a nice woman. She has two workers to help move furniture. There is a place to groom pets next to the furniture store. It is called Clark's Cuts and Kennels.

The doctor and the vet are far from the center of town. They are small, but they help the people of Johnston. There is one elementary school. Children go to a school in another town for middle and high school.

There are no parks in town, but they are making a park. It will be two and a half acres.

There is not much to do in town. There are no movies, bowling, or places to play. But it is a nice town. It is small.

I first heard of my place on a radio show. It was about people who went missing. It was a surprise. The rent is very high here. I did not know this story. My friends did not know it either. Maybe it is hard to live here. I know some friends cry at night. Things are expensive, but we learn to save money. We like old toys and clothes from the past. We smell less as we grow older. We might smoke, or we might just get used to things. But old things are always around. The smell of being an adult is old magazines on a piano. It stays on your things even after you wash them. There are three stores where you can buy used things near my home. If you walk far, you can go to two charity stores, a library, a store with old books, and a store with strange things. The city center is busy. Cars and people are everywhere in the morning. But you cannot hear them in the stores. No matter how many people pass by, the stores are quiet. It is a good place to spend an afternoon. Every year, there are more cars and people. It is growing, they say. One big company that sells things online is here. It is still growing. It reminds me of New York. Everyone is busy with their own plans. No one asks much of you. You can be alone and quiet, and people will leave you alone. It is not like the South, where people care a lot about each other. Here, people do not ask about your life. You can stay quiet if you want, and the city will go on as always. It is a good place to live. There is always something happening. The person next door plays the piano, and there are two people upstairs who like to sing. We are like a group of friends. We help each other when we need it. We celebrate birthdays and funerals. I am lucky to live here. I like most of my neighbors. They are good to me. I clean up after myself and share food with them. They do the same. We help each other with mail. It is nice to see them. I think they like me, and I like them. I live in a big, cold building, but my neighbors make me feel like my life is not bad.

My town is like many other towns. Many houses are alike. There is a group that looks after the houses. We call it the homeowner's association.  The houses are nice and clean.  The yards are small with grass, rocks, and short driveways. Most houses have two garages. The roads are new and in good shape. There are not many old houses here. Most are one story, but some are two stories.

We do not have mailboxes in front of each house. Instead, there are many mailboxes at the end of the street.  People use a key to get to their mail. There are also big boxes for packages.

My house is near the edge of the city.  It feels like a mix of the city and the country. We have a lot of space. There are several pools that people can use. There are also paths for walking.

Most of the people here are older. It is a safe place. People look out for each other. There are also some younger families here.

The city is big, but it feels small. We have what people need. There is one mall. It is not very big, but it has stores. It takes me fifteen minutes to drive to the mall. There are many stores there. We have stores for people who want good food and stores that sell things for less money.

My town is safe and clean. It is a good place to live. It is not very exciting, but it is comfortable.

I live in a small town. It is near a big city. My home is on the east side of town. This side is not rich. Houses are old. Many people here have little money. But my neighbors are good. They say hello when I walk by. There is some crime here, but not much. A few years ago, there were some shootings near my home. One man died. My neighbors lost their son in a shooting. It was sad. We have not had any problems, but things have gone missing from our porch.

Our town has been hurt by drugs. Many people have died from taking too much medicine. There are places to help people who need help with drugs. They teach people how to help their friends and family.

My son goes to a good school. The teachers are kind. He is happy there. There are many events at the school for parents and children. The school gives free food to all the children because many families are poor. All children are treated the same.

The city has made the town look nicer. They fixed the roads and parks. But they did this mostly in the center of town, not where I live.

I like living here. People are friendly. The schools are good. There are stores to buy things. Our house is not big, but it is comfortable. We have lived here a long time and we like it.

My area is full of people from many places. It is on a hill, with old buildings. I live in a tall building near an old theater. There is a small bar down the street. People like to go there in the summer. 

There is a big park near my home. It is small for the city. In the winter, some homeless people find shelter near the park. They put up tents together to stay warm. They can walk to a center where they can take a bath.

I like my city. The buildings are old and nice. But I like the people most. This area was bad in the past. Gangs were a big problem. People remember when the police were trying to stop the gangs. 

Now, people work hard to keep the area clean. They care about their home. Some people say that white people should not walk alone here at night. I think this is from the past. 

I am not white. People here treat me well. They see me as one of them. I see the problems in the world. I see how people judge others. I know that people should not be judged.

I love my home. The people here are kind. They help each other. I feel safe here.

I live in a small town in Michigan. This town is in the countryside. There are farms and small towns near me. There are no big cities here. There are no big stores, like Walmart or Target. You must drive to go shopping.

My town is very pretty. It is near two lakes: Lake Michigan and Lake Charlevoix. There are beaches everywhere.

My neighborhood is small and quiet. The houses are old and different. Some are new, but most are from a long time ago. The houses have basements. You can see them from the street.

Many houses have yards. Some yards have trampolines and swings. Some people have gardens. Many houses have fences for their animals. The houses look like houses in the middle of America. People here work hard to support their families.

Children play in the streets. People walk dogs, ride bikes, and skate. Neighbors know each other.

The lawns are kept nice. There are no piles of leaves. The grass is cut short. Plants and bushes are trimmed.

This neighborhood is not very fancy. It is nice. People want to raise families here. It is quiet and safe.

There is a police station and a jail nearby. The health office is next door. The recycling center is down the road. People use these services.

There are baseball and softball fields. You can hear the announcers calling the game. The airport is nearby. You can hear small planes taking off and landing.

You can walk to get ice cream. You can walk to the town center. My children can ride their bikes to the park. It is only a few blocks away.

This is a great place to live.
